Directed by Coodie. Chike Ozah.

Written by J. Ivy.

Cast Naeem Ghefari( Naeem Ghefari). Justin Bieber( Self). Kid Cudi( Self). Michael Novogratz( Self). Brandy Crow( Self). Gary Lewis II( Man in 2020 Campaign background). 88 Keys( Self). Takashi Murakami( Self)

Language English.

Producers Mike Beck. Lynne Benioff. Carmen Cee. Marjorie Clarke. Alexa Conway. Kate Ferraguto. Ross Martin. Ian Orefice. Peter Pham. Connor Schell. Kern Schireson. Rebecca Teitel. Leah Natasha Thomas. Kevin Thomson. Nick Tran. Angus Wall. Coodie.

Production Creative Control. Leah Natasha Productions. Time Studios.

 

Number of Seasons 1

Number of Episodes 3

Status Finished (2022–2022)
